summary: Adds A New Craftable Sword To Skyrim Poseidon\'s Wrath
descriptionHtml:
Weapons Of The Gods 
---------------------------
Adds A New Craftable Sword To Skyrim Poseidon\'s Wrath
----------------------------------------------------------------------
A blade forged deep beneath the ocean, that, when it strikes, it destorys them with the power of the sea.
---------
Craftable under the glass section at the forge.
And requires the perks arcane smithing and glass smithing
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
It has high stats and speed, and a frost encnantment
I play with OCS, Warzones, Deadly Dragons, Sky MoMod, Mo spawns, Monster wars, so the stats may be a bit high for some of you.
author: SDD707
